data.description: Back on Market! Buyer Financing fell through! Welcome to the beautiful community of Country Walk where all you need is your home and fishing pole! Upon entering the home you are greeted by an open floor plan living room/ dining space with plenty of natural light. The attached bonus area is bright with already installed shelving. The kitchen has plenty of counter space and solid wooden cabinets for storage to help you stay organized. The master bedroom has his and hers closets as well as a private bathroom. This home has an attached two car garage for your convenience. In the back yard you will find a paved path to your very own workshop with electrical that is a great space for hobbies. Country Walk community not only offers boat parking on Lake Carrie but also a club house that offers planned activities to keep you entertained and in touch with your neighbors.
